Description:
    Stubs in files for a ViewComponent of a Heroicon's svg paths (heroicons.com)

Example:
    bin/rails generate heroicon:component SomeIconName

    This will create:
        app/components/heroicon/outline/some_icon_name_component.rb
        app/components/heroicon/outline/some_icon_name_component.html
        app/components/heroicon/solid/some_icon_name_component.rb
        app/components/heroicon/solid/some_icon_name_component.html
